### DESCRIPTION ###
a config repository to save me time when ricing arch linux(i3wm)

### HOWTO ###
install flameshot, vim, kitty, rofi, feh, thunar, polybar, flatpak, spotify and build abba23/spotify-adblock(last 2 are optional, but remove the spotify alias from .bashrc)
run all afromentioned apps to generate cofig files
replace the original config files with the respective modified ones, or simply add the config files 
add wallpaper.jpg to ~/.resources/ and /etc/resources
replace stock ~/.bashrc with the modified version(make sure to add a dot in front of the github one's filename when replacing)

(optionals)

install lightdm-slick-greeter and lxappearance
configure lightdm to use lightdm-slick-greeter, specify the background path as /etc/resources/wallpaper.jpeg

### ESSENTIAL ###

import the meme folder

### END OF FILE ###
